MlDomain.description: The TaskBot Intent Set is a structured collection of defined scenarios that empower the chatbot to understand user needs and execute corresponding actions efficiently. Each intent represents a specific task or request, enabling the bot to deliver context-aware responses and streamline automated workflows across diverse use cases. This setup ensures the chatbot performs with precision and adaptability, enhancing user engagement through intelligent intent recognition and action execution.
